query:
SELECT ass.id, ass.assetId, a.name as assetName, p.id as projectId, p.userId, p.company
FROM assessments ass
INNER JOIN assets a ON ass.assetId = a.id
INNER JOIN projects p ON a.projectId = p.id
WHERE ass.deletedAt IS NULL
  AND (ass.hidden = 0 OR ass.hidden IS NULL)
LIMIT 5;
